➜搭载英特尔技术的首颗AI人造卫星已被送入太空轨道
http://www.sohu.com/a/426354943_447115	56525
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201021/d3681b7a3f2047598f6565bec1ab863c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
